               <msContents>
                  <summary>Amharic Commentary on Our Father, የአቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ትርጓሜ፡, Notes on orders of the rite of baptism and the Mass, in Amharic</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from = "1r" to = "41v"/>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                     <title>Amharic Commentary on Our Father</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang = "amh">
                       በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ብሎ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ እንዲጀምር፡ ጌታችን፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አንትሙሰ፡ ሶበ፡ ትጸልዩ፡ ከመዝ፡ በሉ፡ አለ፡...
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from = "41v" to = "42v"/>
                    <title>Notes on orders of the rite of baptism and the Mass, in Amharic</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang = "amh">
                      እጽሕፍ፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ቀዳሽ፡ ቢታጣ፡ ጥምቀት፡...
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
